==English==

===Verb===
'''praught'''
# {{rfv}} ''(non-standard):'' Irregularly formed past tense of ''to [[preach]]'', in a manner similar to ''[[teach]]/[[taught]]''.  Apparently a modern jocular construction but taken seriously by some.

[[Category: English verbs]]

